name: Champagne & Gold Table Numbers with Ribbon/Rhinestone Heart Embellishment
description:
This listing is for One (1) Table Number (one sided).

Simple & Elegant...this table number is made of metallic paper...Opal, Gold & Ice Gold. The embellishments include rhinestone buckle with satin ribbon.

***Matching Invitations & Placecards also available***

All table numbers are handmade to order and can be completely customized. If you prefer a different color, send me a message so we can discuss.
